{"tid":231601,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AV尾上若葉登台　巨乳「洗臉」男粉高潮惹！","createTime":"2017-05-06T07:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T09:55:22.000Z","uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89deba07c855ba880b0edf3924ad461478eb2ca6","tid":231601,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"24歲H奶日本AV女優尾上若葉今天來台，宣傳她出道以來的首本寫真集《陽尾》，已來台多次的她，在下午舉行的見面會上福利大放送，以保鮮膜隔著胸部，讓粉絲在尺度範圍下近距離和她有肌膚之親，感受她波霸上圍的溫暖，她說：「這本寫真集以我的笑容為賣點，希望大家會喜歡。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她在粉絲見面會上，安排愛的抱抱、膝枕等互動橋段，現場還抽出幸運粉絲送上原味內褲，粉絲還將內褲套在頭上，當場變身「瘋狂假面」，將現場氣氛帶到最高潮。尾上表示很喜歡台灣，現在正在學中文，希望之後有機會來台發展。明天她將舉辦攝影會，讓參加粉絲親眼見證她最性感動人的一面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170506/640_e1548a3106ae475f63f6ccbd05d00f05.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170506%2F640_e1548a3106ae475f63f6ccbd05d00f05.jpg&h=4508ef1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170506/640_507a65a72d11a2eb5b232b8784e57927.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170506%2F640_507a65a72d11a2eb5b232b8784e57927.jpg&h=c3b59e0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170506/640_860d0a0acde17bf607c3c23988102640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170506%2F640_860d0a0acde17bf607c3c23988102640.jpg&h=7f20f1cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56a68044cbc0ba19ab319fb1dcecad0fd8a7f85d","tid":231601,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T07:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"